QuestData.Title: WANTED: Lord Ha'kass
QuestData.Description: Wanted for attacks against the Alliance!$b$bLord Ha'kass is responsible for leading several raids and ambushes against our soldiers.$b$bLast seen near the vicinity of this command poster.$b$bExtreme caution advised!$b$bUpon completion of the mission, report to Lieutenant Hawkins for commendation.
QuestData.LogDescription: Retrieve the head of Lord Ha'kass.
